      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KINGSBRAE REX (1) has a strong record this trip with three wins and four placings from eight starts. In the money last time at this track (23.67) in a Grade 4, finishing a 8 length third. Has the ability and should feature. MRS. JACOBS (8) caught the eye with a fast early split and setting up a 2 length win at Taree Super Track over 300m in 17.30. Can make it two on the bounce. SWAY BAR (2) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 5 at this track. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. HOOTIN' ANGEL (5) is building a nice picket fence and can add to the tally.",
